# == Class: php::fpm::service
#
# Configure fpm service
#
# === Parameters
#
# [*service_name*]
#   name of the php-fpm service
#
# [*ensure*]
#   'ensure' value for the service
#
# [*enable*]
#   Defines if the service is enabled
#
